    <item>
      <title>大选后谨慎买家涌现，法国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/french-stocks-decline-after-surprise-leftist-win-banks-weaken</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国股市上涨，扭转了早盘的跌势，因为在左翼政党意外获胜、议会出现分裂且没有明显多数的情况下，投资者将选举结果视为“最不坏”的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/french-stocks-decline-after-surprise-leftist-win-banks-weaken</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 07:17:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国僵局缓和极端情况，股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/euro-slips-after-french-vote-as-busy-week-begins-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市上涨，因为人们对法国大选结果的最初担忧导致人们乐观地认为政客们可以组建一个更为温和的联盟来遏制极右翼势力。欧元抹去了损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/euro-slips-after-french-vote-as-busy-week-begins-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 22:36:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国议会投票结果不明朗 投资者忧心忡忡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/markets-may-warm-to-french-result-after-initial-shock-analysts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国提前举行的立法选举未导致任何政党在国民议会中获得多数席位，尽管投资者警告称，随着政治僵局临近，未来几周市场将出现动荡，但法国股市周一上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/markets-may-warm-to-french-result-after-initial-shock-analysts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 21:26:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
